7 An Act relating to alcoholic beverages; defining
terms; making certain actions by an employee not
8 attributable to licensed establishments; providing an
affirmative defense under certain circumstances;
9 requiring licensed establishments to present certain
information when asserting the affirmative defense;
10 attributing certain actions by an employee to the
licensed establishment; creating a rebuttable
11 presumption that a licensed establishment has
indirectly encouraged violations of the law by
12 employees; authorizing the ABLE Commission to present
evidence to establish a rebuttable presumption;
13 stating which party has the burden of persuasion;
providing construing provision; providing for
14 codification; and providing an effective date.
