17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
19 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 6-130 of Title 37A, unless there
20 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21 As used in this section:
22 1. "Employee" means any person paid by an establishment
23 licensed by the Alcoholic Beverage Laws Enforcement (ABLE)
24 Commission to sell, serve, dispense, or deliver alcoholic beverages
